# No Plan File Edits

When user attaches a plan (`.plan.md`, roadmap, "Implement the plan"):

1. **Read plan** — do not modify it
2. Use existing todos if already created
3. Implement in plan order
4. Summarize shipped work vs plan at end

If plan is stale vs codebase, report mismatch — ask user to update plan; don't edit it yourself.

Skill: `plan-implement-only` (personal: `~/.cursor/skills/plan-implement-only`)
